			<P>“The vision must be followed by the venture. It is not enough to stare up the steps; we must step up the stairs”-Vance Havner  </P>
			
			<P>As a pediatrician and someone who cares about the health of the population, I find it useful to understand how we can make changes in our lives. 
			During the COVID-19 pandemic, we all struggled to stay healthy both physically and mentally as we were in lockdown. In some parts of the world, 
			lockdowns are still ongoing but in other parts like in the US, we are getting out of lockdown. </P>
		
